    <div class="sec-num">§ 1.0 — Overview</div>
    <div class="sec-title">Research Focus Areas</div>
    <div class="sec-rule"></div>
    <div class="research-topics">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-num">Area 01</div>
        <div class="topic-title">Dynamic Path Planning</div>
        <div class="topic-desc">Robot navigation in unknown environments using skeleton-guided wave propagation algorithms.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-num">Area 02</div>
        <div class="topic-title">EGF Skeletonization</div>
        <div class="topic-desc">Four-stage skeleton extraction: Wave Propagation → Fat Skeleton → 1-Pixel → Local Thinning.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-num">Area 03</div>
        <div class="topic-title">Image Processing</div>
        <div class="topic-desc">Digital image processing applied to robotics, medical imaging, and autonomous systems.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-num">Area 04</div>
        <div class="topic-title">NLP &amp; Graph Theory</div>
        <div class="topic-desc">Network topology G(N,E) encoding using NLP for machine learning graph-based models.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
     PAGE: ABOUT
═══════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="page-about" class="page">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="pg-num">§ 2.0 — Biography</div>
    <h1>About Me</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <div class="sec-num">§ 2.1 — Profile</div>
        <div class="sec-title">Md Hasibuzzaman</div>
        <div class="sec-rule"></div>
        <p>I am a graduate researcher and Ph.D aspirant at Asia University, Taiwan, pursuing my M.E. in Computer Science and Information Engineering with a perfect GPA of 4.30/4.30. My research is conducted at the Big Data Lab, focused on robotics, dynamic path planning, and image processing for autonomous mobile robots.</p>
        <p>My core thesis investigates skeletonization-based on object wave propagation for mobile robot navigation in unknown environments — developing novel collision avoidance algorithms that combine Euclidean distance transforms with topological skeleton extraction (EGF four-stage method).</p>
        <p>I am a recipient of the prestigious <strong>Taiwan Ministry of Education (MOE) Scholarship 2024</strong>, recognizing academic excellence in my graduate program. Prior to graduate studies, I completed B.Tech in Electrical &amp; Electronics Engineering at Lovely Professional University, India (GPA 8.18/10) with multiple international exchange programs.</p>
        <div class="badge-group">
          <span class="ieee-badge">Robotics</span>
          <span class="ieee-badge">Path Planning</span>
          <span class="ieee-badge">Image Processing</span>
          <span class="ieee-badge">NLP</span>
          <span class="ieee-badge">Graph Theory</span>
          <span class="ieee-badge">Python</span>
          <span class="ieee-badge">C / C++</span>
          <span class="ieee-badge">R Language</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-block">
        <h3>Contact Information</h3>
        <div class="contact-items-wrapper">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="c-label">Institution</div>
            <div class="c-val">Asia University, Taiwan</div>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="c-label">Department</div>
            <div class="c-val">CS &amp; Information Engineering</div>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="c-label">Lab</div>
            <div class="c-val">Big Data Lab</div>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="c-label">Location</div>
            <div class="c-val">Wufeng, Taichung, Taiwan</div>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="c-label">Email</div>
            <div class="c-val"><a href="mailto:hsbuzzaman@gmail.com">hsbuzzaman@gmail.com</a></div>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="c-label">LinkedIn</div>
            <div class="c-val"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/md-hasibuzzaman-57818b1aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">md-hasibuzzaman-57818b1aa</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/md-hasibuzzaman-57818b1aa" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="linkedin-btn">
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
          Connect on LinkedIn
